<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<bug>
    <id>409790</id>
    <title>[Drag n drop] Image for dragged items doesn't disappear when droping into IE</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">User-Agent:       Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; fr; rv:1.9b2) Gecko/2007121120 Firefox/3.0b2
Build Identifier: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; fr; rv:1.9b2) Gecko/2007121120 Firefox/3.0b2</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">When you drag and drop an item (for instance text) from Firefox to Internet Explorer, the image which is following your cursor during the operation doesn't disapear when you release the mouse button.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.2">So this image is keeping frozen on the screen above all the applications till Internet Explorer is closed.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">Reproducible: Always</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">Steps to Reproduce:</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.2">1 Launch Firefox</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.3">2 Open one page</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.4">3 Select some text</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.5">4 Launch Internet Explorer</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.6">5 Open one page with textboxes or similar components</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.7">6 Drag the selected text from Firefox</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.8">7 Drop the text into the Internet explorer page.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="5">
            <sentence id="5.1">-&gt; The image of dragged item is keeping frozen</sentence>
            <sentence id="5.2">Actual Results:</sentence>
            <sentence id="5.3">The image illustrating the dragged item still appears frozen above IE and any other application.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="6">
            <sentence id="6.1">Expected Results:  
The image disappears when you release the mouse button.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="7">
            <sentence id="7.1">IE version : 6.0.2600.0000</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
